00:05:28.316 --> 00:05:31.306 A:middle
that tells you how
the app feels.

00:05:31.816 --> 00:05:35.406 A:middle
Especially as we start to look
at content front and center

00:05:35.406 --> 00:05:40.206 A:middle
in apps, the motion of this
