00:07:18.966 --> 00:07:21.496 A:middle
something about these
screens almost being stacked

00:07:21.496 --> 00:07:22.456 A:middle
on top of one another.

00:07:23.676 --> 00:07:25.946 A:middle
But if we slow it down
and really take a look

00:07:25.946 --> 00:07:27.696 A:middle
at what's going on,
there's some subtlety

00:07:27.696 --> 00:07:32.256 A:middle
to this animation that's
reinforcing what's happening

00:07:32.296 --> 00:07:33.286 A:middle
as the user is going back.

00:07:34.766 --> 00:07:36.476 A:middle
So watch as I press
the Back button now.

00:07:37.136 --> 00:07:40.446 A:middle
You can see that the label

00:07:40.506 --> 00:07:43.136 A:middle
