attention to it, it's there.

00:07:53.746 --> 00:07:55.466 A:middle
The third reason to animate is

00:07:56.636 --> 00:07:58.996 A:middle
to help connect people's
behavior

00:07:59.386 --> 00:08:00.776 A:middle
to what's happening on screen.



00:07:59.386 --> 00:08:00.776 A:middle
