00:08:44.226 --> 00:08:47.456 A:middle
I can see what is happening
and what's going to happen.

00:08:47.456 --> 00:08:50.386 A:middle
I get a hint about
what's going to happen.

00:08:50.386 --> 00:08:53.356 A:middle
And then if I flick
back up or flick down,

00:08:53.356 --> 00:08:56.376 A:middle
it will either cancel or
complete this gesture.

00:08:57.386 --> 00:08:59.636 A:middle
And the animation will
respond appropriately.



00:09:00.946 --> 00:09:04.426 A:middle
